name: Dance of Oblivion
description:
from the collection of "outside: people we do not see" 
people who are neither beautiful nor famous, who are born in the slums and live in the shadows and die in darkness. people who born in areas out of sights. Their beauty is forgotten in the backyard as their dreams fade away under the wrinkles of their faces and the calluses of their hands. Real people … people who we do not see.
